We checked in with many bags and were not offered help from the valets or the front desk with carrying the bags or offering a trolly to push them to our room.	Called the night before arriving and spoke with the manager (Tim) who was so sweet to take our request (a river view) into consideration.	If you can look past minor issues and alert the hotel staff when there are problems, then it will be worth it to book here.	The staff was very helpful, we arrived at 10 am and got to check in early and the concierge helped us figure out where to eat lunch and where to begin our day.